DefaultReaderConfiguration.fullDescription: Collects events from the following series of Blue Coat ProxySG appliances: 210, 300, 510, 600, 810, 8100, and 9000.

file.toolTipText: Directory or path to read from

string.toolTipText: Hostname of the nDepth appliance to receive log data

integer.toolTipText: Port number of the nDepth appliance to receive log data

select.toolTipText: Data routing (normalized alerts to Manager and/or raw data to nDepth)

integer.toolTipText: Number of seconds between log reads

FastPattern.description: ServiceWarning: {60004} Received unknown URL beginning with query

FastPattern.pattern: ProxySG: 80000 Service TCP_Tunnel:[\d.]+:\d+ send-client-IP is disabled.

FastPattern.description: ServiceInfo: {90000} NTP time matches system clock
FastPattern.matcher: (\d+) ([-\w.]+) ProxySG: (\S+) (NTP: Periodic query of server) ([^,]+), time ([\w ]+)\..*

FastPattern.description: ServiceInfo: {90000} NTP time within acceptable variance
FastPattern.matcher: (\d+) ([-\w.]+) ProxySG: (\S+) (NTP: Periodic query of server) ([^,]+), time ([^,]+), ([^.\(]+).*

FastPattern.pattern: ProxySG: 90000 NTP: (?:Receive timeout|Time out of sync|Wrong originate|DNS error)

FastPattern.description: ServiceWarning: {90000} NTP warning - Tried all configured servers

FastPattern.pattern: ProxySG: 90000 NTP: Response received from wrong NTP Server: [\d.]+ is not [\w.]+

FastPattern.description: ServiceInfo: {E0009} Access log, no log data
ServiceInfo: {140002, CFSSL} Trust package installation done
FastPattern.pattern: ProxySG: 140002 CFSSL: Trust package installation done

FastPattern.description: ServiceInfo: {140002, CFSSL} Automatic update of trust package initiated
FastPattern.matcher: (\d+) ([-\w.]+) ProxySG: (\d+) (\S+): Automatic update \((.*)\) of trust package initiated.*
FastPattern.pattern: ProxySG: 140002 CFSSL: Automatic update \(.*\) of trust package initiated

FastField.defaultValue: Automatic update of trust package initiated
Automatic update of trust package initiated

FastPattern.pattern: ProxySG: 140002 CFSSL: Updated ca-cert '[^']+' since it has been modified in the factory image

FastPattern.description: ServiceWarning: {1F0000} Connection denied due to connection limit

FastPattern.description: ServiceWarning: {1F0000} Connections have dropped to connections
FastPattern.pattern: ProxySG: 1F0000\b\s*Connections for [-\w.]+ have dropped to \d+ connections\. \d+ connections were denied due to connection limit being exceeded

FastPattern.description: ServiceWarning: {250034} Unable to read machine password

FastPattern.description: ServiceWarning: {3B0003} General error communicating with Active Directory
FastPattern.pattern: ProxySG: 3B0003\s*General error communicating with Active Directory

FastPattern.description: ServiceWarning: {430001} Could not send request data
FastPattern.pattern: ProxySG: 430001 Could not send request data

FastPattern.description: ServiceWarning: {45000B} Could not load host key

FastPattern.pattern: ProxySG: 45000C (?:Closing connection to|Connection from|Connection closed by)
ProxySG: 45000C.*?Did not receive identification string from

FastFormatter.condition: Did not receive identification string from ([\d.]+)
FastFormatter.format: Did not receive identification string from "$6"
